{"about_the_game":"Lus\u00f3fona Games Collection 2024 is a curated bundle showcasing the best student projects developed during the past academic year at Lus\u00f3fona University. This collection highlights five games created in events and project classes within the Videogames bachelor\u2019s degree program. Play the games and watch the developer commentary to take a behind-the-scenes look at our students' journey to becoming the next generation of videogame developers.<br><br>Featured games:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Inside Poetry Remastered - First Year<br></li><li>Human Ltd. - Second Year<br></li><li>Magical Intern - Second Year<br></li><li>PodScape - Second Year<br></li><li>Shades of Insanity - Third Year</li></ul><br>Please be mindful that these game experiences are small vertical slices that showcase the essential features and gameplay elements, but do not represent final products.<br><br>Hope you enjoy them as much as we do!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004070/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1721377740","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004070/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1721377740","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004070/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1721377740","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004070/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1721377740","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"There are several games in the launcher but only one of them, \"Shades of Insanity\", is a horror game that delves into sensitive mental health themes. In this game, you play as a patient coping with a mental illness that induces visual and auditory hallucinations."},"detailed_description":"Lus\u00f3fona Games Collection 2024 is a curated bundle showcasing the best student projects developed during the past academic year at Lus\u00f3fona Uni